# Known divergence (by design): CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE emits an extra WARNING +
# HINT because unlogged data is not replicated; see
# docs/query_serving/unlogged_tables.md. Real COPY behavior differences in this
# test are intentionally left unpatched.
